<heading>inbox - List unplaced notes.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  inbox
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Lists all notes that have not been placed in any box.
</paragraph>

<paragraph>
Notes start in the inbox after creation. They remain
there until placed somewhere with note put.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
Examples
</heading>

<pre>
inbox
  List all unplaced notes.

note/inbox
  From another space, qualify the path.
</pre>

<paragraph>
Use inbox to see which notes still need a place.
Place them with note put.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
add, delete, edit, list, man, put, remove, show
</paragraph>
